European Union Public Licence v1.2 — Change License
----------------------------------------------------

After the Change Date, the Licensed Work converts automatically to the
European Union Public Licence v1.2 (EUPL-1.2). From that date on, the
work may be used, modified, and distributed under the terms of the
EUPL-1.2 without further restriction.

Full EUPL-1.2 license text:
https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/collection/eupl/eupl-text-eupl-12

EUPL © the European Union 2007, 2016


Per-Version Change Dates
------------------------

Each Vivodepot version converts to EUPL-1.2 four years after its release
date. The Change Date above applies to the version named in this file.
Earlier and later versions carry their own Change Dates in their
respective release commits.

  Version            Released      Change Date
  ----------------   -----------   -----------
  1.0.0-beta.16      2026-05-01    2030-05-01
  1.0.0-beta.15      2026-04-21    2030-04-21
  (earlier betas)    see CHANGELOG.md

Once a version's Change Date has passed, that version is permanently
EUPL-1.2-licensed and may be used by anyone, including for commercial
purposes, without further consent.


